  ],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "The Budget Act of 2022, the Budget Act of 2023, the Budget Act of 2024, and the Budget Act of 2025 made appropriations for the support of state government for the 2022\u201323, 2023\u201324, 2024\u201325, and 2025\u201326 fiscal years, respectively.\n\nThis bill would amend those budget acts by amending, adding, and repealing items of appropriation and making other changes.\n\nThis bill would declare that it is to take effect immediately as a Budget Bill."
    }
  ],
